    • Method Detail

      • next

        void next(Parent parent,
          SourcePosition startPosition,
          SourcePosition middlePosition,
          SourcePosition endPosition)
        Called at every step when an emojicode program is run.
        Parameters:
        parent - the parent of the current emojicode part that is to be executed.
        startPosition - the start position of the emojicode part that is to be executed now.
        middlePosition - the middle position of the emojicode part that is to be executed now. This could for example be a method call, there the method and the class is on the left and the parameter list is on the right of this point.
        endPosition - the end position of the emojicode part that is to be executed now.

      • programFinished

        void programFinished()
        Called if the program has finished. The program has not finished if it is aborted or if there is a program error.
